### Prod Login as Business (Implicit ADMIN role)
# @name prodLoginBusiness
POST {{prodBaseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "brandstart@demo.zyntra.com",
  "password": "Zyntra2025!"
}

### Prod Get Menu Tree (requires prodLoginBusiness first to set cookie/session)
GET {{prodBaseUrl}}/auth/menus
Content-Type: application/json

